{"tid":801204,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港官：外國有冇人問起大灣區？ 莫乃光：其實係冇","createTime":"2018-08-31T12:19:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T23:09:12.000Z","uid":20058,"like":49,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"a99c2a2a99654c18f9c0048d11c36625f6cbf175","tid":801204,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T12:19:48.000Z","msg":"民主派立法會議員「岳少」楊岳橋同莫乃光，本月初到美國矽谷拜訪多間國際企業後，今日同記者分享所聞。莫乃光話，此行發現國際公司眼中，最關心唔係本港有幾多稅務優惠，而係能否請到合適同足夠的人才。岳少話，同外國投資基金交流時，有問對方會否介紹公司來港發展時，即時「被打臉」，因為全個矽谷都知Uber喺香港被判犯法，「政府吸引人去香港，跟住一棍打番你返去」，認為如要搞好創科，一定要有新法律配合。<br />\n莫乃光跟住補充，話此行發覺好多城巿的官員提及新加坡，令佢知道新加坡喺矽谷有好高位置，吸引投資者方面十分進取。岳少就問過呢啲官員，過去有無接待過來自香港的官員時，對方都話「無乜印象」，反而新加坡同一啲大陸省巿就有，令佢對香港情況有啲焦急。<br />\n莫乃光返港後，原來亦有同政府朋友分享見聞，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">引述本港官員都有問起「外國多唔多人問起大灣區發展？」，佢就好老實咁回覆：「其實係無」</span></span>，認為香港自己品牌同優勢，即係一國兩制、資訊自由、法治，以及智識產權保障，先係最吸引外國投資者的原素，未來應更好發揮。<br />\n咁港府將來點先可以做好啲？莫乃光認為，政府要一改各自為政、以及太被動的陋習，強調「要有智慧城巿，先要有智慧政府」，預告稍後同岳少去英國考察後，就會出份返報告交代見聞同建議，希望可以令香港未來有更好的創科發展喎。  h<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180831/58630739\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180831%2F58630739&d=kDEuW%2BW1JaXomLAtNExz510Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=e0a15505\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180831%2F58630739&h=67604129\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180831/58630739</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1b3eb42370e70fd715bfa8699462051191f83a8","tid":801204,"uid":42764,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T12:22:21.000Z","msg":"創科?是日最大笑話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53771c543013d084e2eb2f9a2be7802ab69c153a","tid":801204,"uid":132859,"like":38,"dislike":2,"score":36,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T12:23:59.000Z","msg":"uber 單嘢已經係死罪啦<br />\n仲想昆人投資大灣區<br />\n係咪傻㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e4705dec7e516875779896cc66c95df04c6ee65","tid":801204,"uid":15880,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"53771c543013d084e2eb2f9a2be7802ab69c153a","tid":801204,"uid":132859,"like":38,"dislike":2,"score":36,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T12:23:59.000Z","msg":"uber 單嘢已經係死罪啦<br />\n仲想昆人投資大灣區<br />\n係咪傻㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T12:26:50.000Z","msg":"的士佬對香港政府咁重要<br />\n有咩事可以用黎代警察郁手, 扮交通意外殺平民<br />\n<br />\n梗係打走你uber 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"917c12f554b8131eece226e067b4fb14deb5672f","tid":801204,"uid":76310,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T12:28:58.000Z","msg":"摩天輪，正苦成人鴿棍都得<br />\n惟有博鬼佬唔知<br />\n<br />\n大灣區又係搵水魚"},{"pid":"a542da85001b189dfd081b74cf8a0a7afbb96262","tid":801204,"uid":22535,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T12:29:30.000Z","msg":"大媽區<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1232a8ea3431719df7ce0820e6f73c1be4f4f8b4","tid":801204,"uid":48973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T12:29:38.000Z","msg":"叫林鄭同包子去大灣住包保有人識"},{"pid":"6cfd0381dd63dc25d77edefd914ac8b61f2a2648","tid":801204,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T12:31:23.000Z","msg":"宜家政府根本係殭化！"},{"pid":"785616c0cc374c1fecbc6c312757ec8fa4fd3369","tid":801204,"uid":113000,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T12:32:28.000Z","msg":"玩完<br />\n壞印像已經俾人定型<br />\n有排洗底"},{"pid":"84df8d